Addvise receives allocation decision from Kuopio University Hospital
Wednesday, 15 Feb 2017 08:40am EST 
Addvise Group AB (publ) : Receives allocation decision from Kuopio University Hospital in Finland worth 1.8 million Swedish crowns ($200,000) .Agreement has a standstill period until Feb. 17 2017. 
			
Full Article





ADDvise gets order from Consto worth NOK 2.9 million
Tuesday, 14 Feb 2017 05:45am EST 
ADDvise Group AB (publ) : ADDvise receives order from Consto AS worth 2.9 million Norwegian crowns ($346,554) . Its unit LabRum AB has signed agreement with Consto AS for delivery of pass through cupboards to PET center in Tromsø, Norway .Order will be delivered during second and third quarters of 2017. 
			
Full Article





ADDvise: Allocation decision from Region Skåne of SEK 1.7 million
Friday, 14 Oct 2016 07:18am EDT 
ADDvise Group AB : Says subsidiary ADDvise Tillquist AB has received allocation decision from Region Skåne worth 1.7 million Swedish crowns ($197,145) . Agreement has standstill period until Oct. 24 .Order is for delivery of large low temperature freezers and low temperature freezers designed to reduce energy consumption. 
			
Full Article





ADDvise receives order from SLL worth SEK 4.8 mln + option of SEK 3.3 mln
Monday, 22 Aug 2016 04:34am EDT 
ADDvise Group AB : ADDvise subsidiary LabRum AB has received an allocation decision by Stockholm County Council (SCC) to deliver 100 CO incubators to NKS (New Karolinska Solna) and an option of another 66 CO incubators . The order amounts to 4.8 million Swedish crowns ($572,089.20) and the value of the option amounts to 3.3 million crowns which gives a total value of 8.1 million crowns . The order will be delivered during 2016 and the option during 2017 .The agreement has a standstill period until August 29, not until then LabRum AB has the right to sign the agreement with SLL. 
			
Full Article





Addvise Q2 EBIT rises to SEK 9.2 million
Thursday, 18 Aug 2016 02:46am EDT 
Addvise Group AB : Q2 order intake 53.6 million Swedish crowns ($6.4 million) versus 46.1 million crowns year ago . Q2 net sales 54.1 million crowns versus 37.4 million crowns year ago .Q2 EBIT 9.2 million crowns versus 3.1 million crowns year ago. 
			
Full Article





ADDvise signs agreement worth about NOK 4.3 million
Monday, 27 Jun 2016 07:29am EDT 
ADDvise Group AB : Signs agreement with Consto AS worth about 4.3 million Norwegian crowns ($504,535) . subsidiary LabRum AB has signed agreement with Consto AS to deliver laboratory furnishings to UNN, the University Hospital of North Norway in Tromsø .Delivery will take place during Q2 and Q3 2017. 
			
Full Article





ADDvise signs SEK 1.2 mln deal with Peab Sweden
