ADDvise Group AB : Q1 net sales 45.7 million Swedish crowns ($5.49 million) versus 41.0 million crowns year ago . Q1 EBITDA loss 1.6 million crowns versus profit 5.5 million crowns year ago .Q1 order intake 33.1 million crowns versus 50.1 million crowns year ago. 
			
